title: Camp WeWow Magic Week Day 5
description:
It's the last day of camp here at Camp WeWow! Today, we're featuring your camper call-ins around the Camp WeWow campfire! You can redeem your Magic Week badge at tinkercast.com/camp, and share what you discovered with us this summer at tinkercast.com/share! Safe travels, campers!
